Building and Installing
=======================

In order to build and install the COMP Superscalar framework:

Execute ./install.sh path_to_install_COMPSs

ex: ./install.sh /home/user

For detailed information on the use of COMP Superscalar, please download the manual from the website:
http://www.bsc.es/compss

